@startuml
' IOD(2)_Pj2_T-1 — User Story 2: Search and Filter Classes
' Author: MayfairMI6

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #444444
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA

title IOD(2)_Pj2_T-1\nUS2: Search and Filter Classes

note right: Author: MayfairMI6

start

:Actor navigates to the Search & Filter Classes Page;
note right: Prerequisite: at least one\nsemester's data is imported

:Actor enters one or more search criteria\n(course code, instructor, semester, department);

#ADD8E6:**ref** UC_SEARCH — Search and Filter Classes
─────────────────────────────────────────────
System queries the database and returns matching classes;

if (Results found?) then (yes)
  :System displays list of matching classes\n(title, section, instructor, room, times, enrollment);

  if (Actor selects a specific class?) then (yes)
    #ADD8E6:**ref** UC_DETAILS — View Class Details
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
    System displays full attributes of the selected class;
    :Actor reviews detailed class information;
  else (no)
    :Actor reviews search result list;
  endif

else (no)
  :System displays "No results found" message;
  :Actor adjusts criteria and retries;
endif

stop
@enduml
